Title: 5 Excel Macros Every Social Media Manager Needs to Reclaim 5 Hours a Week

Introduction: If you think 'Macros' are only for finance bros and data scientists, think again. In 2026, the most successful Social Media Managers are using automation to handle the heavy lifting of data analysis.

Macro 1: The Multi-Platform Cleaner: Stop manually deleting columns from your Meta and TikTok exports. This macro standardizes every CSV into one master sheet instantly.

Macro 2: The Best Posting Time Predictor: Forget generic 'best time to post' articles. This macro analyzes your specific audience engagement peaks and highlights your optimal posting windows.

Macro 3: The Automated ROI Calculator: Input your ad spend and conversion data, and let this macro calculate your cost-per-acquisition across every platform.

Macro 4: Keyword Sentiment Analysis: Use AI to categorize your comments into positive, neutral, or negative, giving you a pulse on brand sentiment without reading every single message.

Macro 5: The One-Click Monthly Report: The holy grail. A macro that pulls data into a pre-formatted, client-ready dashboard with one click.

How to Get Started: You don't need to learn VBA to use these. Our AI-Powered tool generates these macros for you based on simple English prompts.

